{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_011MWE8H6Axvt1fiWDRsjpzC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Both paths are verified working. Here's the summary.\n\n## Done — both endpoints are live and verified\n\n**DB Console — `https://crdb-ui.example.com` (TLS)**\n- The CockroachDB cluster runs with `--insecure`, so the Console backend is plain HTTP on port 8080. TLS is therefore terminated at the ingress.\n- Created TLS secret `crdb-ui-tls` (self-signed cert, CN/SAN `crdb-ui.example.com`) in the `cockroachdb` namespace.\n- Created Ingress `crdb-ui` (class `nginx`, `backend-protocol: HTTP`) routing `crdb-ui.example.com` → `crdb-cluster-public:8080`.\n- ✅ Verified: `curl -k https://crdb-ui.example.com/` through the controller returns **HTTP 200**.\n\n**SQL — TCP port 26257 via ingress-nginx**\n- SQL is the PostgreSQL TCP wire protocol, not HTTP, so it can't use an Ingress object. Used ingress-nginx's TCP passthrough instead:\n  - ConfigMap `ingress-nginx/tcp-services`: `\"26257\": \"cockroachdb/crdb-cluster-public:26257\"`.\n  - Added `--tcp-services-configmap=$(POD_NAMESPACE)/tcp-services` to the controller args.\n  - Added containerPort `26257` to the controller pod and port `26257` to the `ingress-nginx-controller` Service.\n- ✅ Verified: controller listens on `0.0.0.0:26257`, and a real `cockroach sql` query against `ingress-nginx-controller:26257` returned `sql-via-ingress-ok`.\n\n**Note on external access:** the `ingress-nginx-controller` LoadBalancer shows `EXTERNAL-IP: <pending>` (no cloud LB / MetalLB in this cluster), and `--publish-status-address=localhost`, so the Ingress has no external address. Inside/at the cluster everything is reachable via the controller Service (NodePorts 32274/32277 for 80/443). For real external use you'd point `crdb-ui.example.com` DNS at the controller's ingress IP and add a node-level path for 26257 — but the ingress configuration itself is complete and proven functional."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":585,"cache_read_input_tokens":33856,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":585},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"bdfaefc9-4690-47e6-819c-6f1526268015","uuid":"cccf2080-e122-4ba9-8dec-d4c7ecfd6352","request_id":"req_011CcAoht6mC3C7qsfyPHtA2"}
